---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '../components/CTABand.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Why Choose VS Furnitures | Trusted Carpenter & Contractor in Indore"
  description="Quality furniture within your budget — not cheap. No commission. End-to-end solution. Strong old market network. We never leave a project unfinished. VS Furnitures, Indore."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Why Us</p>
      <h1>Why Choose VS Furnitures?</h1>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
      <p class="hero-sub">30+ years. 700+ kitchens. One promise — quality furniture, complete transparency, zero hassle.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CORE STATEMENT -->
  <section class="section core-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="core-block reveal">
        <p class="core-text">
          We build <span class="hl">high-quality furniture within your budget</span> — and when we say that, we do not mean cheap. We mean that every rupee you spend goes into the quality of your furniture, not into hidden margins or commissions from hardware shops.
        </p>
        <p class="core-text mt">
          If you are looking for someone who will take care of your home interior <span class="hl">completely — without leaving it in the middle</span> — who is <span class="hl">reliable, trustworthy</span>, who has the right connections in the market to get you the best material on priority, without dragging you from shop to shop just to earn a brokerage — then you have found the right team.
        </p>
        <p class="core-text mt">
          We are an <span class="hl">end-to-end solution</span>. Once you connect with us, you do not need to go anywhere or call anyone else. And through our <span class="hl">strong old network</span> built over 30 years, we can arrange what you can dream of for your home.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- KEY DIFFERENTIATORS -->
  <section class="section diff-section texture-bg">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">What Makes Us Different</p>
      <h2>Six reasons our clients keep coming back</h2>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
      <div class="diff-grid">

        <div class="diff-card diff-card--featured reveal">
          <div class="diff-num">01</div>
          <h3><span class="gold-text">No Commission. No Brokerage.</span></h3>
          <p>Many contractors earn a secret cut — called <em>brokerage</em> — from hardware shops every time they bring a client there. We do not take a single rupee of commission from any shop. Every shop we recommend, we recommend because the material is right — not because we earn from it. You pay the actual market price, not an inflated one.</p>
          <div class="diff-tag">Zero brokerage. Zero hidden cuts.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card diff-card--featured reveal">
          <div class="diff-num">02</div>
          <h3><span class="gold-text">We Never Leave a Job in the Middle.</span></h3>
          <p>This is something many local contractors fail at — they start strong and vanish. Once we begin a project, we see it through to the end. We have completed over 700 kitchens and 150+ full home fit-outs across Indore. Not one left unfinished. Your project gets a confirmed completion date before we start — and we deliver on it.</p>
          <div class="diff-tag">100% project completion. Every time.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card diff-card--featured reveal">
          <div class="diff-num">03</div>
          <h3><span class="gold-text">Strong Old Network.</span> 30 Years of Connections.</h3>
          <p>We have built relationships with timber traders, ply suppliers, hardware dealers, and craftsmen across Indore over three decades. This network means we can access quality materials not available at most local shops — and get them faster, at better prices, because of trust built over years. If you can dream it for your home, we can find it.</p>
          <div class="diff-tag">Market access most contractors don't have.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card reveal">
          <div class="diff-num">04</div>
          <h3><span class="gold-text">Quality Under Budget.</span> Not Cheap.</h3>
          <p>There is a clear difference between affordable and cheap. Cheap means low-grade ply, poor hardware, corners cut where you cannot see. Affordable means every rupee going into material quality and craftsmanship — not wasted. Our furniture lasts 15–20 years because we never compromise on what goes inside it.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card reveal">
          <div class="diff-num">05</div>
          <h3>End-to-End Solution</h3>
          <p>One call. One team. One point of contact. You do not coordinate a separate person for measurement, another for materials, and a third for fitting. We handle the full project — design, sourcing, building, and installation. From the day you call to the day you live in your furnished home.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="diff-card reveal">
          <div class="diff-num">06</div>
          <h3>Reliable &amp; Trustworthy</h3>
          <p>We have served Indore families for over 30 years. Our reputation is our business. We show up on time, do what we say, and are honest about what is possible within your budget. If something is not achievable, we tell you — and suggest the best alternative. No false promises. No surprises.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROOF NUMBERS -->
  <section class="section proof-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="proof-grid reveal">
        <div class="proof-stat">
          <span class="stat-num">30+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Years in Indore</span>
        </div>
        <div class="proof-stat">
          <span class="stat-num">700+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Kitchens Built</span>
        </div>
        <div class="proof-stat">
          <span class="stat-num">150+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Homes Furnished</span>
        </div>
        <div class="proof-stat">
          <span class="stat-num">0</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Projects Left Incomplete</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand heading="Ready to work with a team you can trust?" sub="Call or WhatsApp for a free site visit — no obligation, no commission, just honest advice." />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.page-hero { background: var(--navy-deep); padding: 96px 0 64px; text-align: center; }
.page-hero h1 { color: var(--white); font-size: clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem); }
.page-hero .eyebrow { display: block; }
.page-hero .gold-line { margin: 1rem auto 1.5rem; }
.hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 1.05rem; }

.core-section { background: var(--white); }
.core-block { max-width: 820px; }
.core-text { font-size: 1.12rem; line-height: 1.85; color: var(--ink); }
.mt { margin-top: 1.25rem; }
.hl {
  background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(194,162,74,0.18) 0%, rgba(194,162,74,0.18) 100%);
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold);
  padding: 0 0.15em;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--navy);
}

.diff-section { background: var(--paper); }
.diff-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
.diff-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid rgba(16,37,66,0.08); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
.diff-card--featured { border-left: 4px solid var(--gold); }
.diff-num { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(194,162,74,0.25); line-height: 1; }
.diff-card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--navy); line-height: 1.4; margin: 0; }
.diff-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; }
.diff-card em { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }
.diff-tag { display: inline-block; background: rgba(194,162,74,0.12); color: var(--navy); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 3px; margin-top: 0.25rem; }
.gold-text { color: var(--gold); }

.proof-section { background: var(--navy); }
.proof-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 2rem; text-align: center; }
.proof-stat { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
.stat-num { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); line-height: 1; }
.stat-label { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; }

@media (max-width: 900px) { .diff-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
@media (max-width: 600px) { .diff-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .proof-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; } }
</style>
